OL,6,FHowever, police say that despite
OL,7,Fthorough investigations over the last
OL,8,Ftwo decades, the assault on Leon, who
OL,9,Fwas also robbed of his wages, remains
OL,10,Fundetected.
OL,12,FNow detectives are hoping a renewed
OL,13,Fpersonal plea from Leon's mum Angela
OL,14,Fand the announcement of a cash reward
OL,15,Ffrom Crimestoppers who help encourage
OL,16,Fanyone with information to come
OL,17,Fforward.
