OL,6,FThe charity is offering up to #20,000
OL,7,Ffor information that leads to the
OL,8,Fconviction of those responsible for
OL,9,Fattack.
OL,11,FLeon's mum Angela Main said: "I had
OL,12,Ftwo sons with Leon, I had the son that
OL,13,Flived for 24 and a half years, that
OL,14,Fwas like the rest of us, had a normal
OL,15,Flife, ran around, loved computers,
OL,16,Floved drawing and all those things.
OL,18,F"And then, one day I just didn't have
OL,19,Fhim.
